{"word":"H7809 - שָׁחַד - shâchad - shaw-khad' - Hire","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">שָׁחַד</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>shâchad"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>shaw-khad'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Hire"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - வெகுமானம், கொடு, பணையங்கொடு"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"(Qal) to give a present, to bribe, to ransom, to offer gifts"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> A primitive root; to <i>donate</i>, that is, <i>bribe: - </i>hire, give a reward."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H7809 - שָׁחַד - shâchad - shaw-khad'/7809\">H7809</a>, <a href=\"#/H7810 - שַׁחַד - shachad - shakh'-ad/7810\">H7810</a>"}]}